<p>Reports erroneous relations in Docker Compose files.</p>
<p>
  According to the <a href="https://docs.docker.com/reference/compose-file/services/#volumes">Compose file specification</a>,
  certain fields may be invalid depending on the other key-value pairs and may cause errors.
</p>
<p>
  For example, one such relation is volume <code>source</code> field, which is invalid when the volume <code>type</code> is <code>tmpfs</code>.
</p>
